<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.1">
<l>ūṉēṟu celvat tuṭaṟpiṟavi yāṉvēṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>āṉēṟēḻ veṉṟā ṉaṭimait tiṟamallāl</l>
<l>kūṉēṟu caṅka miṭattāṉṟaṉ vēṅkaṭattuk</l>
<l>kōṉēri vāḻuṅ kurukāyp piṟappēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will not desire birth in a body, the wealth of which [consists in having] flesh that builds up,</l>
<l>but the state of servitude for Him who subdued the seven bulls.</l>
<l>I shall be born as a heron living in the Kōṉēri [lake] in Veṅkaṭa</l>
<l>of Him who has a conch that is curved to [His] left.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
